Step.SQLStatement: CREATE VIEW RV_S_ContractDetail AS SELECT cl.AD_Client_ID, cl.AD_Org_ID, cl.IsActive, cl.Created, cl.CreatedBy, cl.Updated, cl.UpdatedBy, c.S_Contract_ID, c.DocumentNo, c.POReference, c.DocStatus, c.DocAction, c.C_DocType_ID, c.IsApproved, c.IsCreditApproved, c.SalesRep_ID, c.Bill_BPartner_ID, c.Bill_Location_ID, c.Bill_User_ID, c.IsDropShip, c.AD_User_ID, c.IsSOTrx, c.DateDoc, c.DateContract, c.DateSigned, c.DateAcct, c.DurationGrace, c.DurationUnitGrace, c.DateDeadline, c.DateApproved, c.DatePrinted, c.DaysToExpiry, c.PP_Calendar_ID, c.PP_PeriodDefinition_ID, c.DeliveryRule, c.PriorityRule, c.DeliveryViaRule, c.FreightCostRule, c.Weight, c.Volume, c.InvoiceRule, c.PromotionCode, c.M_PriceList_ID, c.IsDiscountPrinted, c.PaymentRule, c.C_PaymentTerm_ID, c.PlannedQty, c.PlannedAmt, c.CommittedQty, c.CommittedAmt, c.TotalLines, c.GrandTotal, c.Processed, c.IsPrinted, c.IsDelivered, c.IsInvoiced, c.Issummary, c.IsSelfService, cl.Line, cl.Link_ContractLine_ID, cl.Ref_ContractLine_ID, cl.S_ServiceType_ID, cl.R_StandardRequestType_ID, cl.C_ServiceLevel_ID, cl.C_BPartner_ID, cl.C_BPartner_Location_ID, cl.IsIndefinite, cl.IsRecurrent, cl.FrequencyType, cl.Frequency, cl.RunsMax, cl.RunsRemaining, cl.DateNextRun, cl.DateLastRun, cl.DateStartSchedule, cl.DateFinishSchedule, cl.DateStart, cl.DateFinish, cl.DateDelivered, cl.DateInvoiced, cl.Duration, cl.DurationUnit, cl.DurationRequired, cl.DurationEstimated, cl.C_Campaign_ID, cl.C_Project_ID, cl.C_Activity_ID, cl.AD_OrgTrx_ID, cl.C_ProjectPhase_ID, cl.C_ProjectTask_ID, cl.User1_ID, cl.User2_ID, cl.User3_ID, cl.User4_ID, cl.S_ContractLine_ID, cl.M_Product_ID, cl.S_ResourceAssignment_ID, cl.Description, cl.M_Warehouse_ID, cl.M_AttributeSetInstance_ID, productAttribute(cl.M_AttributeSetInstance_ID) AS ProductAttribute, pasi.M_AttributeSet_ID, pasi.M_Lot_ID, pasi.GuaranteeDate, pasi.Lot, pasi.SerNo, cl.C_UOM_ID, cl.QtyEntered, cl.QtyOrdered, cl.QtyReserved, cl.QtyDelivered, cl.QtyInvoiced, cl.PickedQty, cl.C_Currency_ID, cl.PriceActual, cl.PriceEntered, cl.FreightAmt, cl.C_Tax_ID, cl.PP_Period_ID, cl.IsConsumesForecast, cl.M_FreightCategory_ID, cl.M_Promotion_ID, cl.M_Shipper_ID, cl.QtyOrdered-cl.QtyDelivered AS QtyToDeliver, cl.QtyOrdered-cl.QtyInvoiced AS QtyToInvoice, (cl.QtyOrdered-cl.QtyInvoiced)*cl.PriceActual AS NetAmtToInvoice, cl.QtyLostSales, cl.QtyLostSales*cl.PriceActual AS AmtLostSales, CASE WHEN PriceList=0 THEN 0 ELSE ROUND((PriceList-PriceActual)/PriceList*100,2) END AS Discount, CASE WHEN PriceLimit=0 THEN 0 ELSE ROUND((PriceActual-PriceLimit)/PriceLimit*100,2) END AS Margin, CASE WHEN PriceLimit=0 THEN 0 ELSE (PriceActual-PriceLimit)*QtyDelivered END AS MarginAmt, p.M_Product_Category_ID, p.M_Product_Class_ID, p.M_Product_Classification_ID, p.M_Product_Group_ID, cc.C_Charge_ID, cc.C_ChargeType_ID, bp.C_BP_AccountType_ID, bp.C_BP_SalesGroup_ID, bp.C_BP_Segment_ID, bp.C_BP_IndustryType_ID, cl.LineNetAmt , cl.UUID FROM S_Contract c INNER JOIN S_ContractLine cl ON (c.S_Contract_ID=cl.S_Contract_ID) INNER JOIN C_BPartner bp ON(bp.C_BPartner_ID = cl.C_BPartner_ID) LEFT JOIN M_Product p ON(p.M_Product_ID = cl.M_Product_ID) LEFT JOIN C_Charge cc ON(cc.C_Charge_ID = cl.C_Charge_ID) LEFT OUTER JOIN M_AttributeSetInstance pasi ON (cl.M_AttributeSetInstance_ID=pasi.M_AttributeSetInstance_ID);

The record is active in the system

There are two methods of making records unavailable in the system: One is to delete the record, the other is to de-activate the record. A de-activated record is not available for selection, but available for reports. There are two reasons for de-activating and not deleting records: (1) The system requires the record for audit purposes. (2) The record is referenced by other records. E.g., you cannot delete a Business Partner, if there are invoices for this partner record existing. You de-activate the Business Partner and prevent that this record is used for future entries.
